OL,3,CSTV News ceases production at
OL,4,CEdinburgh studio
OL,6,GQuietly and with no ceremony, there
OL,7,Ghas been a significant change to the
OL,8,Gformat of the STV News at 6.
OL,10,FAn innovative format which saw the
OL,11,Fprogramme co-presented from both
OL,12,FGlasgow and Edinburgh has been dropped.
OL,14,FThere is now just one presenter based
OL,15,Fin Glasgow.
OL,17,FThe sub-opt bulletin for the Edinburgh
OL,18,Farea remains but is presented from
OL,19,FGlasgow.
OL,21,FNothing is said on-air to draw
OL,22,Fattention to the sub-opt.
