OL,6,FThe change in the presentation
OL,7,Ftechnique marks a significant change
OL,8,Fin the character of the programme
OL,9,Fthough.
OL,11,FCo-presenters John Mackay and Kelly-
OL,12,FAnne Bishop had a warm on-screen
OL,13,Frelationship even though they were 50
OL,14,Fmiles apart.
OL,16,FThe old format also helped deal with
OL,17,Fthe traditional rivalry between
OL,18,FScotland's two big cities.
OL,20,FIt was hard to accuse STV of west
OL,21,Fcoast bias with one co-presenter in
OL,22,FEdinburgh together with a sub-opt.
