OL,6,FCleverly, the opening sequence and the
OL,7,Ffirst link were often tailored so that
OL,8,Fto viewers in the east the Edinburgh
OL,9,Fpresenter appeared to be taking the
OL,10,Flead ` while viewers in the west saw
OL,11,Fthe Glasgow presenter.
OL,13,FIt was an innovative, if perhaps
OL,14,Fcomplex, arrangement. It will be
OL,15,Finteresting to see if the changed
OL,16,Fformat affects the ratings.
OL,18,FThe new format will certainly be
OL,19,Feasier to handle logistically.
