OL,6,FHaving said all that, the story of
OL,7,FSTV's sub-regions is an interesting
OL,8,Fone. You can debate whether or not
OL,9,Fthey are really effective.
OL,11,FSTV only started to split advertising
OL,12,Fbetween the east and west of the
OL,13,FCentral Belt in the late-90s.
OL,15,FA news sub-opt followed around 2006.
OL,17,FFor a period the east even had an
OL,18,Fentirely separate programme and a
OL,19,Fdistinctive late-night bulletin after
OL,20,FNews at Ten.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
