OL,6,FSimilarly a few parts of the Central
OL,7,FBelt with more in common with Glasgow
OL,8,Fget the Craigkelly signal.
OL,10,FWhile the Edinburgh opt is definitely
OL,11,Fa boost to viewers there, the scale of
OL,12,Fthe area covered by the Glasgow
OL,13,Fservice makes a localised service for
OL,14,Fviewers in the west harder.
OL,16,FThe STV West region is huge `
OL,17,Fcovering, for example, the West
OL,18,FHighlands and many of the islands off
OL,19,Fthe Argyll coast.
OL,21,FThe STV News has always had an
OL,22,Finteresting remit.
