OL,3,CSTV News ceases production at
OL,4,CEdinburgh studio
OL,6,FAt one level, it is a regional news
OL,7,Fprogramme for Central Scotland. At
OL,8,Fanother, it competes with the BBC to
OL,9,Fprovide Scottish national news.
OL,11,FThe STV News sometimes includes
OL,12,Fstories of importance from the rest of
OL,13,FScotland.
OL,15,FSimilarly it is not always possible to
OL,16,Fneatly define a Glasgow or Edinburgh
OL,17,Fstory as "local" or "national".
OL,19,FHopefully though the new format will
OL,20,Fmake it cost-effective for STV to
OL,21,Fcontinue to tailor its output for
OL,22,Fdifferent parts of Central Scotland.
